级斗争又进入","box":[[71,890],[636,889],[637,909],[72,910]]},{"text":"了新的高潮。","box":[[72,922],[187,922],[187,943],[72,943]]},{"text":"385","box":[[583,968],[616,968],[616,987],[583,987]]}],"dimensions":{"height":1060,"width":709}}